replies.body:
What Mutley said and;

The stats on it are well rounded, although early flat AP is better on most mids. However it allows you to get all of your following items significantly quicker. It's unbalanced on some champions, for example Ahri, that can survive early game easy and don't need flat damage to have an impact.

It's similar to Avarice Blade (rip) in that the stats are pretty good but not amazing, but the gold income sets up your next items.
